org.judal.storage.table

Class AbstractIndexableTableOperation<R extends Record>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.judal.storage.table.AbstractTableOperation<R>
      • org.judal.storage.table.AbstractIndexableTableOperation<R>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, Operation
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractRelationalOperation

    public abstract class AbstractIndexableTableOperation<R extends Record>
extends AbstractTableOperation<R>

    Base class for indexable table operation wrapper.

    Be sure to always call close() after an operation is done or else a connection leak may occur.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Sergio Montoro Ten
